data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautifully remodeled residence is eagerly awaiting the perfect family to create lasting memories. From the moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and spacious living environment that has been thoughtfully updated to meet modern needs. This home boasts four generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for family members and guests. A convenient main floor bedroom offers flexibility and accessibility for various living arrangements. The second floor features a master bedroom with an ensuite, offering a private and luxurious retreat. Additional two bedrooms on the second floor ensure everyone has their own comfortable space. Enjoy the versatility of a loft area, perfect for creating a home office, playroom, or relaxation spot. The full finished basement is a blank canvas ready for your creativity, whether you envision it as an entertainment area or home gym. This home sits on a double lot, providing a vast outdoor space, ideal for a family with children or those who love outdoor activities. With a 3-car garage and alley access, parking and storage are a breeze. Whether you're relaxing in the elegant living space, enjoying the convenience of the main floor bedroom, or exploring the possibilities of the full finished basement, this home offers it all.
